#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
End-to-end trainer: COCO (val-only) rehearsal + WaterFilter new class.
- Downloads only val2017 (~1GB) + annotations into your requested path
- Converts to YOLO .txt
- Ensures WaterFilter labels use class id 80
- Optionally oversamples WaterFilter via symlink clones
- Writes combined YAML (81 classes)
- Trains Ultralytics YOLO

Notes:
- If WaterFilter has no `images/val` (and/or `labels/val`), we reuse
  its `images/train` (and implicitly `labels/train`) as the validation split.

Requires: pip install ultralytics tqdm requests
"""

